		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston</placeName> <date>May 27<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1830</date>.</p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Mr. Leeser</addressee>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Your favour with the<lb/> accompanying Paper came safe to hand.  I<lb/> read your communication with much pleasure&#44;<lb/> your reply is inanswerable&#44; and your quotations<lb/> in support of your opinions pointedly appropriate.<lb/>  I doubt not your work will be read with<lb/> interest by all denominations.</p>
			<p rend="indent(12)"><persName>Mr. Harrison</persName><lb/> the bookseller who has kindly given publicity<lb/> to your circular&#44; informed me that should<lb/> you send him a few copies he will dispose<lb/> of them charging you only a commission.  He<lb/> further states&#44; that many christians would<lb/> purchase who are averse to have their names<lb/> attached to a subscription paper.  I cannot<lb/> flatter you with an account of many<lb/> subscribers&#44; <persName>Nat Hart</persName> your friend obtained<lb/> many who could have placed their names<lb/> on my paper.  Which by the by is just the<lb/> same.  I have shown him and others<lb/> your communication in the <placeName>Richmond</placeName> Whig<add>&#63;</add>&#8212;<lb/> and they are all highly pleased.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>as yet there are only three or four names<lb/> to your circular&#44; as the number will be<lb/> small&#44; I shall omit sending you the<lb/> list at the time you mention.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I regret to learn the illness of<lb/> <persName>Miss Etting</persName>&#44; I hope she will recover&#8212;<lb/> My Respects to all Friends and<lb/> accept the wishes of</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Your Friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">&#40;In Haste<add>&#63;</add>&#41;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">Jacob De La Motte</persName></p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)">The <addressee>Revd. Mr. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">per Brig</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Langdon chi<add>&#63;</add>&#41;.</p>
		</body>
